      "writtenOn": "2018-09-18T18:26:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As mentioned in the previous comment, multiple simultaneous requests for the same task do not trigger new compilation runs, it instead uses the existing compilation runs.\nBut, if the compilation run is finished for this issue+patchset then we want to trigger a new run. This is done by deleting the file from GCS (which contains all previous updates which no longer apply) and creating a new file.",
